Package: quickshell
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         qt6-qpa-plugins,
         qml6-module-qtquick,
         qml6-module-qtquick-controls,
         qml6-module-qtquick-window
Recommends: qt6-svg-dev
Description: QtQuick-based Wayland/X11 desktop shell toolkit
 Quickshell is a simple and flexible QtQuick-based desktop shell toolkit
 for Wayland and X11. It provides a powerful environment for creating
 custom desktop shells, bars, panels, widgets, and other desktop
 components using QML.
 .
 Features include:
  - Wayland support (wlroots layershell, session lock, etc.)
  - X11 support
  - Hyprland-specific integrations
  - i3/Sway IPC support
  - System tray (StatusNotifier)
  - PipeWire integration
  - MPRIS media player control
  - PAM authentication
  - Polkit agent support
  - And more

